mbedded":true},{"title":"bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_11_229_231_234_255_0.jpg","target":"images/bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_11_229_231_234_255_0.jpg","line":443,"embedded":true},{"title":"bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_11_136_600_363_308_0.jpg","target":"images/bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_11_136_600_363_308_0.jpg","line":447,"embedded":true},{"title":"bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_12_1127_223_399_278_0.jpg","target":"images/bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_12_1127_223_399_278_0.jpg","line":471,"embedded":true},{"title":"bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_12_1142_624_318_243_0.jpg","target":"images/bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_12_1142_624_318_243_0.jpg","line":485,"embedded":true},{"title":"bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_14_1141_1262_316_230_0.jpg","target":"images/bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_14_1141_1262_316_230_0.jpg","line":641,"embedded":true},{"title":"bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_21_216_1019_262_255_0.jpg","target":"images/bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_21_216_1019_262_255_0.jpg","line":897,"embedded":true},{"title":"cos $\\left( {\\pi  + \\alpha }\\right)  + \\mathrm{i}$ sin $\\left( {\\pi  + \\alpha }\\right) \\rbrack$ .\n\n## 练习 9.4(1)\n\n1. 下列复数是否用三角形式来表示的? 为什么?\n\n(1)3π(cos 0.5+i sin 0.5)； (2) $2\\left( {\\sin 1 + \\mathrm{i}\\cos 1}\\right)$ ；\n\n(3) $\\cos {131\\pi } + \\mathrm{i}\\sin {131\\pi }$ ； (4) $\\sqrt{2}\\left( {\\cos {0.3\\pi } + \\mathrm{i}\\sin {0.2\\pi }}\\right)$ ；\n\n(5) $- 2\\left( {\\cos \\frac{\\pi }{4} + \\mathrm{i}\\sin \\frac{\\pi }{4}}\\right)$ ； (6) $3\\left( {\\cos \\frac{\\pi }{5} - \\mathrm{i}\\sin \\frac{\\pi }{5}}\\right)$ .\n\n2. 把下列复数用三角形式表示(用辐角主值):\n\n(1) 3; (2)-2i;\n\n(3) $1 + \\mathrm{i}$ ； (4)-1+ $\\sqrt{3}\\mathrm{i}$ .\n\n## 2 三角形式下复数的乘除运算\n\n现在我们讨论三角形式下的复数乘除运算公式.\n\n设有两个用三角形式表示的复数 ${z}_{1} = r\\left( {\\cos \\alpha  + \\mathrm{i}\\sin \\alpha }\\right)$ 与 ${z}_{2} = s\\left( {\\cos \\beta  + \\mathrm{i}\\sin \\beta }\\right)$ ,其中 $r = \\left| {z}_{1}\\right|  \\geq  0, s = \\left| {z}_{2}\\right|  \\geq  0$ ,则\n\nQ\n\n$$\n{z}_{1}{z}_{2} = {rs}\\left\\lbrack  {\\cos \\left( {\\alpha  + \\beta }\\right)  + \\mathrm{i}\\sin \\left( {\\alpha  + \\beta }\\right) }\\right\\rbrack  ;\n$$\n\n$$\n\\frac{{z}_{1}}{{z}_{2}} = \\frac{r}{s}\\left\\lbrack  {\\cos \\left( {\\alpha  - \\beta }\\right)  + \\mathrm{i}\\sin \\left( {\\alpha  - \\beta }\\right) }\\right\\rbrack  \\left( {{z}_{2} \\neq  0}\\right) .\n$$\n\n---\n\n三角形式下的复数乘除运算公式称为棣莫弗公式.\n\n---\n\n![bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_23_251_1624_193_214_0.jpg","target":"images/bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_23_251_1624_193_214_0.jpg","line":969},{"title":"bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_25_579_402_887_307_0.jpg","target":"images/bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_25_579_402_887_307_0.jpg","line":1091,"embedded":true},{"title":"bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_25_221_1468_255_315_0.jpg","target":"images/bo_d4sll53ef24c73be0n1g_25_221_1468_255_315_0.jpg","line":1117,"embedded":true}],"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"last_embed":{"hash":"faettw","at":1773194168633}},"smart_blocks:上海教材md/必修二第9章复数/必修二第9章复数-dollar.md###9.1 复数及其四则运算": {"path":null,"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.06964479,-0.00309191,-0.01353515,-0.02466406,0.01400687,-0.01273318,-0.03080723,-0.02071525,0.0491953,-0.01079337,0.01392375,-0.06531724,0.08369277,0.03040353,0.01323564,-0.00500909,-0.03244813,-0.04795392,-0.05931895,0.01762435,0.07454851,-0.05893324,0.0254171,-0.04419878,0.05465133,0.00687733,0.02093519,-0.01989833,0.00928725,-0.17247859,-0.00484186,0.01697127,0.00658417,0.02175119,0.05397122,-0.0141302,-0.04849183,0.01656397,0.00307722,0.03858257,-0.01868605,0.05202657,0.02856043,-0.0015393,0.04690947,-0.05528563,0.07318836,-0.03162777,0.04943959,-0.02587504,-0.00289633,-0.01734734,-0.00928935,0.04253144,0.04237719,0.00634418,0.04418977,0.07245047,0.00153807,0.00726062,0.05328835,0.05529715,-0.21838462,0.05780435,0.04061605,-0.03949908,-0.00432071,0.04311894,0.02486803,0.06474944,-0.04798086,-0.02771964,0.01543023,0.03558602,-0.01133237,-0.05789834,0.00884893,-0.06795486,-0.02286095,-0.03979025,0.00813615,0.08420654,-0.00020291,-0.01953342,-0.0060